A minimalistic top-down view of a sleek workspace showing a large tablet or touch screen displaying a complex form being divided into smaller, organized card-like sections with clean geometric shapes. Translucent blue and white rectangular panels float and separate from the main screen, suggesting modular breakdown. The color palette is crisp whites, soft grays, and Salesforce-inspired blues. Subtle shadows create depth between the floating form segments. The composition emphasizes order emerging from complexity, with precise grid lines and generous white space surrounding the central device.
